@startuml sequence_report
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Report Generation & Export

actor "Fleet Manager" as User
participant "Angular SPA\n(Kendo UI Charts)" as FE
participant "ReportsController\n(.NET 8+)" as API
participant "ReportGeneration\nService" as RptSvc
participant "ExportService\n(QuestPDF/ClosedXML)" as Export
database "SQL Server 2022" as DB

User -> FE: Select report type,\ndate range, filters
FE -> API: POST /api/v1/reports/fleet-utilization
API -> RptSvc: GenerateFleetUtilization(request)
RptSvc -> DB: Aggregate telemetry data\n(Dapper, <3s target)
DB --> RptSvc: Aggregated results
RptSvc --> API: ReportResponse with DataPoints
API --> FE: JSON report data
FE -> FE: Render Kendo UI\nBar/Pie/Line charts
FE --> User: Interactive charts displayed

== Export ==
User -> FE: Click "Export to PDF"
FE -> API: POST /api/v1/reports/fleet-utilization/export?format=pdf
API -> RptSvc: Re-generate data
RptSvc -> DB: Query
DB --> RptSvc: Data
API -> Export: GeneratePdf(data)
Export --> API: PDF byte stream
API --> FE: File download (Content-Disposition)
FE --> User: PDF downloaded

@enduml
